snippet: The graphite sketch is of a woman among at least 10 whose bodies were found mostly off Ocean Parkway and who may be the victims of a serial killer or killers.
abstract: The graphite sketch is of a woman among at least 10 whose bodies were found mostly off Ocean Parkway and who may be the victims of a serial killer or killers.
lead_paragraph: The graphite sketch is of a woman with light eyes and perhaps sandy hair. Below it is almost all that police know of her: her legs were found in 1996, her skull just last year.

headline.main: Police on Long Island Release Sketch of Woman Whose Skull Was Found Last Year
